msgstr "Configure data approval workflows."

msgid ""
"Data elements are fundamental units for data collection in DHIS2, "
"representing individual data points for both tracker and aggregate data. "
"They serve as the building blocks for capturing, analysing, and reporting "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Data elements are fundamental units for data collection in DHIS2, "
"representing individual data points for both tracker and aggregate data. "
"They serve as the building blocks for capturing, analysing, and reporting "
"information."

msgid ""
"Create, update, view and delete data elements: the foundation of data "
"collection and analysis."
msgstr ""
"Create, update, view and delete data elements: the foundation of data "
"collection and analysis."

msgid ""
"Improve analysis of single data elements by combining them into data "
"element groups."
msgstr ""
"Improve analysis of single data elements by combining them into data "
"element groups."

msgid ""
"Add another level of organisation by grouping data element groups into "
"group sets."
msgstr ""
"Add another level of organisation by grouping data element groups into "
"group sets."

msgid ""
"Data sets are collections of data elements grouped for aggregate data "
"entry, validation, access, collection frequency and reporting. Data entry "
"forms are defined and configured by data sets. They help streamline the "
"management of data collection routines and ensure consistency across "
"different stages of data handling within DHIS2."
msgstr ""
"Data sets are collections of data elements grouped for aggregate data "
"entry, validation, access, collection frequency and reporting. Data entry "
"forms are defined and configured by data sets. They help streamline the "
"management of data collection routines and ensure consistency across "
"different stages of data handling within DHIS2."

msgid ""
"Create, update, view and delete data sets, specify the related data "
"elements, period type organisation units, sharing settings and workflow "
"approval here."
msgstr ""
"Create, update, view and delete data sets, specify the related data "
"elements, period type organisation units, sharing settings and workflow "
"approval here."

msgid "Create, update, view and delete data set notification templates."
msgstr "Create, update, view and delete data set notification templates."

msgid ""
"Indicators are used to calculate and analyze data based on data elements "
"and other indicators. Predictors are used to predict future data values."
msgstr ""
"Indicators are used to calculate and analyze data based on data elements "
"and other indicators. Predictors are used to predict future data values."

msgid ""
"Create, update, view and delete indicators, specify the numerator and "
"denominator, and set the indicator type."
msgstr ""
"Create, update, view and delete indicators, specify the numerator and "
"denominator, and set the indicator type."

msgid ""
"Create, modify, view and delete indicator types. An indicator type is a "
"factor for an indicator, like percentage."
msgstr ""
"Create, modify, view and delete indicator types. An indicator type is a "
"factor for an indicator, like percentage."

